beer.beer_description: This ultra-local lipsmacker features saltbush from Naway Yila Buradja (Mudgee) for a full-flavoured supple gose. Kettle-soured with satisfying savoury notes and sprinkles of rock salt, it's an earthy honest umami treat with specially selected grains rounding out the mouthfeel. Herbaceous. audacious, and downright delicious.
